      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おっと、レコード会社まで行くとはいえ、さすがに\n早く来過ぎたか……すまない、外で時間を潰してくるよ",
      "startTime": 15.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだし、遠慮しないで上がってってよ\n芽衣ね、ちょうど今からおやつタイムなんだー",
      "startTime": 24.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にどうかな？\n美味しい紅茶もあるし、ゆっくりしてこー！",
      "startTime": 29.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確かにまだ一時間以上余裕はあるか……",
      "startTime": 33.1984570343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ芽衣、準備してくるね！\n紅茶に合うおすすめのドーナツ持って来るよー",
      "startTime": 39.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ソファでごろーんって寝っ転がってのんびり待ってて\n今、みんな出掛けてるし、気にしなくて大丈夫だからね",
      "startTime": 46.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6387.098805200005,
          "startTime": 49.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
